</button>
<div class="p-4 bg-white border-t border-gray-100">
<p class="text-gray-600">Our chocolate-covered strawberries are best enjoyed within 24-48 hours of delivery. We recommend refrigerating them upon receipt and bringing them to room temperature for about 30 minutes before serving for the best taste experience.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="mb-6">
<button class="flex justify-between items-center w-full text-left p-4 bg-white rounded shadow-md">
