</button>
<div class="p-4 bg-white border-t border-gray-100">
<p class="text-gray-600">Yes, we offer delivery within a 15-mile radius of our location. For orders outside this area, please contact us directly to discuss options. We also offer pickup from our store. All deliveries are made in temperature-controlled packaging to ensure freshness.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="mb-6">
<button class="flex justify-between items-center w-full text-left p-4 bg-white rounded shadow-md">
