</button>
<div class="p-4 bg-white border-t border-gray-100">
<p class="text-gray-600">Absolutely! We offer various customization options including chocolate type, decorations, packaging, and personalized messages. For special requests or corporate branding, please contact us at least 48 hours in advance of your desired delivery date.</p>
